{
  "name": "Slicer",
  "summary": "<p>每个 <strong>Slicer</strong> 对象都代表工作簿中的一个切片器。切片器用于筛选数据透视表或 OLAP 数据源中的数据。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicers/Slicers .htm#Slicers.Add\">Add</a></strong> 方法可将 <strong>Slicer</strong> 对象添加到 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicers/Slicers .htm#Slicers.Slicers\">Slicers</a></strong> 集合。若要访问表示切片器中当前选中的按钮的 <strong>SlicerItem</strong> 对象，请使用 <strong>Slicer</strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.ActiveItem\">ActiveItem</a></strong> 属性。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿上第一个切片器缓存中第一个切片器的标题更改为“My Slicer”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Caption</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;My Slicer&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿上第一个切片器缓存中第一个切片器的宽度设置为 200 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Width</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表工作簿中的一个切片器。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "ActiveItem",
      "summary": "<p>当指定的切片器有焦点，并且活动的控件是切片器中的按钮时，<strong>ActiveItem</strong> 属性将返回 <strong>SlicerItem</strong> 对象（例如，在此状态下，用户使用键盘切换切片器中的按钮）。</p>\n<p>下面的情况下，<strong>ActiveItem</strong> 属性将返回 <strong>Null</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>指定的切片器没有焦点（未选中或处于非活动状态）。</li>\n<li>指定的切片器有焦点，并且选中的是整个切片器本身（例如，用户可在此状态下使用键盘四处移动整个切片器）。</li>\n<li>指定的切片器有焦点，并且活动的控件是切片器标题中的 <strong>“清除筛选”</strong> 按钮。</li>\n</ul>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/SlicerItem/SlicerItem .htm#SlicerItem.SlicerItem\">SlicerItem</a></strong> 对象，该对象代表指定切片器的当前获得焦点的切片器按钮。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第一个切片器缓存中第一个切片器的焦点中的切片器按钮的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Slicers</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveItem</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例取消选择第一张工作簿上第一个切片器缓存的切片器“name”的焦点中的切片器项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slicer = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Slicers</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;name&quot;</span>)\n    slicer.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveItem</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Selected</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "SlicerItem",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Caption",
      "summary": "<p>为 <strong>Caption</strong> 属性指定的值显示在切片器的标题中。如果未指定 <strong>Caption</strong> 属性，ET 将使用基础 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PivotField/PivotField .htm#PivotField.PivotField\">PivotField</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/PivotField/PivotField .htm#PivotField.Caption\">Caption</a></strong> 属性值。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定切片器的标题。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上数据透视表的第三个切片器的标题。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slicer = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(slicer.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Caption</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作簿上第三个切片器缓存中名为“id”切片器的标题设置为“nameid”。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;id&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Caption</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;nameid&quot;</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ColumnWidth",
      "summary": "<p><strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Slicer\">Slicer</a></strong> 对象的 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Width\">Width</a></strong> 属性根据 <strong>ColumnWidth</strong> 属性和 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.NumberOfColumns\">NumberOfColumns</a></strong> 属性的值自动调整。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>获取或设置切片器控件中每一列的宽度（以磅为单位）。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第二个切片器缓存中第一个切片器每一列的宽度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColumnWidth</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例设置工作表 Sheet1 上第一张数据透视表的第一个切片器每一列的宽度，并显示设置前后的该切片器每一列宽度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slicer = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`设置前切片器每一列的宽度：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${slicer.ColumnWidth}</span> 磅`</span>)\n    slicer.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColumnWidth</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">120</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`设置后切片器每一列的宽度：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${slicer.ColumnWidth}</span> 磅`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（double 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DisableMoveResizeUI",
      "summary": "<p>如果无法通过选择用户界面中的边框或手柄来移动切片器或调整其大小，则为 <strong>True</strong>；否则为 <strong>False</strong>。默认值为 <strong>False</strong>。将 <strong>DisableMoveResizeUI</strong> 属性设置为 <strong>True</strong> 只影响用户界面。不禁用通过从代码中设置 <strong>Slicer</strong> 对象的属性（如 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Top\">Top</a></strong>、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Left\">Left</a></strong>、<strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Width\">Width</a></strong> 或 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Height\">Height</a></strong> 属性）来移动切片器或调整其大小。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置是否可以使用用户界面来移动指定的切片器或者调整其大小。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断活动工作簿上第三个切片器缓存中名为“id”的切片器是否可以使用用户界面来移动该切片器或调整该切片器大小，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slicer = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;id&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (slicer.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisableMoveResizeUI</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;不可以使用用户界面来移动该切片器或调整该切片器大小&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;可以使用用户界面来移动该切片器或调整该切片器大小&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表上数据透视表的第三个切片器设置为不可以使用用户界面来移动该切片器或调整该切片器大小。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slicer = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    slicer.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisableMoveResizeUI</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "DisplayHeader",
      "summary": "<p>如果页眉可见，则为 <strong>True</strong>；否则为 <strong>False</strong>。默认值为 <strong>True</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置显示切片器 <strong><a href=\"./apiObjectTemplate.htm?page=topics/WPS 基础接口/表格 API 参考/Slicer/Slicer .htm#Slicer.Caption\">Caption</a></strong> 的页眉是否可见。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上数据透视表的第三个切片器的标题页眉是否可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;I1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PivotTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayHeader</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿中第三个切片器缓存中名为“id”的切片器的标题页眉设置为不可见。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slicer = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;id&quot;</span>)\n    slicer.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayHeader</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Height",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定切片器的高度（单位磅）。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作簿上第四个切片器缓存中“age”切片器的高度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;age&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表上第一张数据透视表的第一个切片器的高度设置为 200 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slicer = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    slicer.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">200</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（double 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Left",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定切片器在工作表上相对于单元格 A1 左上角的水平位置（单位为磅）。可读/写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表上第一张数据透视表的第三个切片器到单元格 A1 左上角水平位置的距离。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">PivotTables</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Left</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作簿上第一个切片器缓存中“name”切片器的高度设置为 160 磅，并将该切片器到单元格 A1 左上角水平位置的距离设置为 10 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> slicer = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SlicerCaches</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Slicers</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;name&quot;</span>)\n    slicer.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">160</span>\n    slicer.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Left</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（double 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Locked",
      "summary": "<p>如果在工作表受到保护时切片器被锁定，则为 <strong>True</strong>；如果在工作表受到保护时可以修改切片器，则为 <strong>False</strong>。默认值为 <strong>True</strong>。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置在包含指定切片器的工作表受到保护时，是否可以修改该切片器。可读/写。</p>\n",
